      "description": "One visible Beast within 60 feet makes a Wisdom save, with Advantage if the caster or the caster's allies are fighting it; on a failed save, it is Charmed for up to 1 minute, and each time it takes damage it repeats the Wisdom save, ending the spell on itself on a success.",
